  "title": "🌈 Urgent Hiring! Events Sales Crew!",
  "description": "<p>🚀 Ready to Sell Smarter, Market Louder & Grow Faster?</p><p><br />Are you done with boring jobs that don’t get you or your vibe?<br /><br />We’re hiring Sales & Marketing Trailblazers 💡🔥</p><p>Whether you're fresh, a self-taught whiz, or already crushing it in your side hustle — we see you.</p><p><br />What you’ll do:</p><p>🎯 Create campaigns that actually convert</p><p>📈 Own your pipeline (and your growth)</p><p>🤝 Connect with real people, not just leads</p><p>💬 Shape how the brand speaks and shows up online</p><p><br />What we’re looking for:</p><p>✨ Social-savvy, trend-aware thinkers</p><p>🧠 Growth mindset (and meme fluency helps too)</p><p>🚀 Hungry to learn, unafraid to test ideas</p><p>🎙️ Can pitch, persuade, and pivot when needed</p><p><br />What’s in it for you:</p><p>✅ Real responsibility from Day 1</p><p>✅ Mentorship & skill-building (minus the buzzwords)</p><p>✅ Work that actually gets seen</p><p>✅ A team that values your ideas, not just your output</p><p><br />📍[SINGAPORE] | 💼 Entry-mid level | 🕒 Full-time</p><p><br />👉 Slide into our DMs, drop us your CV, or show us your portfolio.</p><p>We're not just hiring — we’re building something. Want in?</p><p><br /> #MarketingJobs #SalesSquad #NowHiring #JoinUs</p>",
